{"tid":1361034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"都係個句，寧得罪拉登","createTime":"2019-07-24T13:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T13:46:46.000Z","uid":272461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34028845f0912ef0372bf441f09536203e697d0c","tid":1361034,"uid":272461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"有內地官媒撐腰、多次發動網上攻擊的內地「帝吧」論壇，昨日突然叫停翻牆到港、聲援香港立法會議員何君堯，原因是他們成員的資料被「高技術人員」起底，不斷收到來自香港的電話騷擾，同時有管理員的個人資料被修改，被改成信奉伊斯蘭教，而且利用他的資料報名參軍。至今日清晨，帝吧更宣佈解散「集團軍粉絲群」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帝吧管理層個人資料被公開後，有成員稱不斷被人電話騷擾：「帝吧很多人都被問候了，打電話來，就馬上掛了，我現在也不敢去外網留言，感覺他們是有『高技術人員』在支持！」另有網民公開截圖，顯示收到大量來自香港的電話問候：「我被港獨問候了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190724&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59856856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190724%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59856856&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0G5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=116ef170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190724%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59856856&h=e760f971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190724&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59856856</a>"},{"pid":"71c143d255351c01a10755fa4bf8b2e43384ca5f","tid":1361034,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"要高技術先搞到你?<br />\n真係以為自己係高科技大國咩支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fb84774a963e4c944a61aa8345e3a5b1f16f3b","tid":1361034,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}